<plot>Kaziuk, a stubborn peasant and his pregnant wife live in a backwood village. The village is once visited by a couple of wanderers, and strange things start to happen afterwards. A new schoolteacher is sent to the area. She stirs erotic fantasies in Kaziuk. In a stir of frustration Kaziuk cuts down a family tree - a sacrilegious act in the eyes of his family. Going a step further and using a scythe for cutting the grass instead of a sickle brings the whole village against him.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?296461</url></doc>
